# AI Marketing Suite — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in values as needed.
#
# Currently, the AI Marketing Suite scripts use only Python stdlib and
# do not require any API keys or secrets to operate. This file exists
# as a placeholder for future integrations (e.g., analytics APIs,
# social media posting, CRM connectors).

# Example: Analytics API key (not currently used)
# ANALYTICS_API_KEY=your-api-key-here

# Example: Social media integration tokens (not currently used)
# TWITTER_BEARER_TOKEN=your-token-here
# LINKEDIN_ACCESS_TOKEN=your-token-here

# Example: PDF report branding
# REPORT_COMPANY_NAME=Your Company
# REPORT_COMPANY_URL=https://example.com
